往案件高，受襲警員首先在廣華醫生檢查到身體擦傷，其後轉到浸會檢查到髗內出血，而被告人夥同犯罪，情節可謂很嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n法庭接受辯方求情指被告人對法律無知，不知道自己行為已構成犯罪。夥同犯每人也要承擔罪責，裁判官認為罪責會因角色而不同，兩名被告沒有出手，突然犯下本案，裁判官以3個月監禁為量刑起點。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"136ee88c236b61e6a43ccade93f274714cb1f852","tid":2207402,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"推 香港警察已被外國政客定性為暴徒、惡霸！ - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2194080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2194080</a>"},{"pid":"199a60a2c284d7af1d38a2b330abe76957ec200a","tid":2207402,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee0c70cf3930aea0a1cf3ec0f8de1bd2ad3619d","tid":2207402,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec2115bf8d84748516462088e8b327874027874","tid":2207402,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:52:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8666892bcb21c9c19117b028b727f25d3c826883","tid":2207402,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:56:05.000Z","msg":"如果計落主犯打到內出血，咁實去到岳巴咁10個月"},{"pid":"59aec93853c2431a34c64716260e1a64cafaed06","tid":2207402,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48dbdb546a7312332c64